U snu me probudio
divan šum nad krevetom.

01:47:03.264 --> 01:47:06.184
Otišla sam do prozora
i na obzoru ugledala

01:47:06.309 --> 01:47:08.603
njegove duge noge kako odlaze.

01:47:09.062 --> 01:47:11.439
